<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>I'm trying to work with the ZfcTwig (<a href="https://github.com/ZF-Commons/ZfcTwig">https://github.com/ZF-Commons/ZfcTwig</a>) module in one of my applications. Everything works, except for mixing up template types.</p>

<p>When trying to use a viewhelper (from a module) which requires phtml files, it fails:</p>

<p>$vm = new ViewModel();
$vm-&gt;setLayout('my/viewfile.phtml');
$this-&gt;getView()-&gt;render($vm);</p>

<p>It can then not find "my/viewfile.phtml" for some reason. I'm pretty sure that the reason for this is the fact that the suffix gets set to .twig in ZfcTwig.</p>

